On or after October 1, 1998, the department of children, youth, and families, or its predecessor agency, has made a founded finding of abuse or neglect of a child against the provider. If the provider has received a certificate of parental improvement under chapter
74.13
RCW pertaining to the finding, the provider is not disqualified under this section;

The department shall adopt rules to implement this section.
